This package adds resource management and exception handling to the @pipes@
ecosystem. Notable features include: * /Resource Safety/: Guarantee
finalization using @finally@, @bracket@ and more * /Exception Safety/:
Even against asynchronous exceptions! * /Laziness/: Only acquire resources
when you need them * /Promptness/: Finalize resources early when you are
done with them * /Native Exception Handling/: Catch and resume from
exceptions inside pipes * /No Buy-in/: Mix resource-safe pipes with
unmanaged pipes using @hoist@

WWW:	http://hackage.haskell.org/package/pipes-safe
